13
00:01:27.920 --> 00:01:31.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
What do you know about France,
you war-shy Gypsy bastard?

14
00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:36.040  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
- So this is the horse?
- And that's the car.

15
00:01:50.840 --> 00:01:52.640  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
